    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The easy way to re-render is indeed to call the Algolia API every N seconds/minutes. If you don't want to go that path you can save the last `renderOptions` and call the `render` function with the saved values + the updated value. Here is [an example](https://codesandbox.io/s/882lr0v159) that show how to implement this solution. It's not the more elegant solution but it works.",
